{"tid":1712911,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"聽日一定要擺工！！！要抗議警隊成個制度！","createTime":"2019-11-12T15:47:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-12T16:03:43.000Z","uid":105590,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"123e5be91ddeb7875268d91c67104f276216b867","tid":1712911,"uid":105590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T15:47:31.000Z","msg":"黑警而家大撚哂！殺人 強姦女仔 酷刑 壞事做盡！真係令我由細到大對警察既價值觀破滅！！<br />\n<br />\n睇到啲黑警話佢地OT咁多 強姦被捕女仔都正常呢句真係覺得好撚冇人性！<br />\n<br />\n我夠日日OT到2046啦 咁係咪就要做返啲喪盡天良既事黎填補心理唔平衡？<br />\n<br />\n根本佢地個本性上面已經有問題 係壞人 同恐怖分子既心態<br />\n<br />\n點解一班咁既人可以做到警察？周圍殺人 強姦女仔就代表正義？<br />\n<br />\n佢地咁樣主動挑釁 入校園殺學生 再暴打班後生仔 再順便告人暴動罪真係睇唔過眼！！<br />\n<br />\nDllm好撚嬲<br />\n<br />\n利申：醫護！雖然有好多病人需要我 但只能講句對唔住！香港到左咁既地步 冇人再可以坐視不理 有咩就同林鄭講 佢同班高官警隊都要付上全部責任！"},{"pid":"4e3b7fe0ce56ac590a33aabb88fa4f64d0f9968a","tid":1712911,"uid":6981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T15:49:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9b3ba8592e70e5a9d87f9f7d749ea695fd79ee81","tid":1712911,"uid":337761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T15:51:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: orange;\">入去retweet like reply</span><br />\n最新：Hawley 出第二條關於中大的tweet!<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/HawleyMO/status/1194269562608463879?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FHawleyMO%2Fstatus%2F1194269562608463879%3Fs%3D20&d=GxO8KwJzUJLP70ptmK1G7Y5RPfZ%2FgKFUZzIsJfjgB6g%3D&h=c5744164\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FHawleyMO%2Fstatus%2F1194269562608463879%3Fs%3D20&h=dd03ffb2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/HawleyMO/status/1194269562608463879?s=20</a><br />\n<br />\n第一條<br />\n（twitter 突發）美國參議員Hawley 為警察攻入中大校園出聲啦！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1712330\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1712330</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n更加多嘅任務同link去 @TwitterHelpBot，admin團隊會繼續更新。"},{"pid":"fccc7111154d3e51275a7a045088edb2bfd203c3","tid":171